## Executive Summary

The implementation introduces 4 new SDUI adapters (DetailHeaderAdapter, TagLabelAdapter, KeyValueRowAdapter, CardActivityAdapter) with mock payloads for order/transaction details and demo stories. The code follows most existing patterns but has **multiple TypeScript type errors** that must be fixed before merge. Missing unit tests also need to be added.

